[[w:Monopoly (game)|Monopoly]] is an American originated family board game played worldwide since the early 20th century. It is published and distributed by [[w:Hasbro|Hasbro]] and [[w:Parker Brothers|Parker Brothers]] today. This book details some rules for monopoly.


This is a collaborative book to which anyone can contribute.  Please see the [[/Project|project]] page for details of current taks.


